                        <Font name="Berlin Sans FB" size="33.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <Label text="Navigate the Floor to land EXACTLY on Boo's Door (Cell 99) with at least 1000 energy. Overshooting wraps you back to the beginning of the board." wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" />
