                        <Font name="Berlin Sans FB" size="33.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <VBox spacing="8.0">
                     <children>
                        <Label text="1. Powerup Phase (Optional): Costs 500 energy." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="2. Dice Roll: Roll a standard 6-sided dice." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="3. Movement: Move to the new cell. If occupied by the opponent, the move is invalid—stay in place and re-roll." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="4. Cell Action: Activate the landed cell's effect." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                     </children>
                  </VBox>
                  
                  <Label alignment="CENTER" contentDisplay="CENTER" prefHeight="20.0" prefWidth="867.0" text="Cell Types" textAlignment="CENTER" wrapText="true">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Berlin Sans FB" size="33.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Label>
                  <VBox spacing="8.0">
                     <children>
                        <Label text="• Doors (One-Time Use): Matching role grants energy to your team. Mismatch drains energy. Doors become exhausted (red bulbs) after the first interaction." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="• Monster Cells: Same role executes your powerup for free. Opposite role swaps energy if you have more than them." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="• Conveyor Belts: Transports you forward." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="• Contamination Socks: Transports you backward and drains 100 energy." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                        <Label text="• Card Cells: Draw a random mysterious Card." wrapText="true">
                           <font><Font name="Cambria" size="25.0" /></font>
                        </Label>
                     </children>
                  </VBox>

                  <Label alignment="CENTER" contentDisplay="CENTER" prefHeight="20.0" prefWidth="867.0" text="Cards" textAlignment="CENTER" wrapText="true">
